{"tid":1554112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"快簽叫美國向叫中共還債或者還香港！","createTime":"2019-09-09T00:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T16:58:52.000Z","uid":20723,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9b01b36c10095319a5dd7769b90b9321ff575d01","tid":1554112,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:25:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pEqbc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pEqbc4.png&h=1f16fd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=uCl2s%2BJteilWOEmp%2BZl8kRTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=e14a7548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a><br />\n<br />\n任何國際之間既債務都有繼承義務<br />\n慈禧簽果條辛丑條約 一戰果時民國繼續還<br />\n仲要還到1938年因爲打二戰窮到pk<br />\n去求條約國唔追辛丑賠款先可以停<br />\n既然中共自稱滿清正統承繼人<br />\n呢張債券自然本利點都要還<br />\n唔還既佢講乜差野要用南京條約去收番香港<br />\n而且美國政府係未同中共追還錢"},{"pid":"fd25702dd3b3686bfa1cb3c68652374643bb2521","tid":1554112,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:32:01.000Z","msg":"你問： 下， 乜美國差大陸錢咩？ 係呀， 大陸揸撚住幾萬億美債， 個D咪美國差大陸錢囉。 攞黎填翻清債條數差唔多架啦。"},{"pid":"cd29a30323ba7db307944972b82582ffe3396dfd","tid":1554112,"uid":20723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:33:57.000Z","msg":"1. 中共還錢既話要燒外匯還(有得傾)<br />\n2. 中共唔還台灣(中華民國)還既話香港回歸台灣(中華民國)<br />\n3. 中共台灣都唔還，美國咪照樣唔還中共D 美債(直接抵美債)<br />\n4. 中共台灣美國都唔做野，債券留番比個孫或者攞去文化博物館"},{"pid":"e59b2dc4c05d0781ee0a05cd0a27fa307256fda4","tid":1554112,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T00:35:08.000Z","msg":"中國稱清朝債券是「中華民國債務」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1553674\" data-auto-link targ